zipkin2.v1

Class V1Span

  • java.lang.Object
    • zipkin2.v1.V1Span
  • Deprecated. 
    new code should use Span.

    @Deprecated
public final class V1Span
extends Object
    V1 spans are different than v2 especially as annotations repeat. Support is available to help migrate old code or allow for parsing older data formats.
